  body
    nav#mainNav.navbar.navbar-default.navbar-fixed-top.affix-top
      .container-fluid
        .navbar-header
          a.navbar-brand.page-scroll(href='#page-top') Michael Perkhofer
        .navbar-right
          ul.nav.navbar-nav.navbar-right
            li
              a.page-scroll(href='#home') Home
            li
              a.page-scroll(href='#portfolio') Portfolio
            li
              a.page-scroll(href='#contact') Contact
    header#home
      p Michael Perkhofer <small>Full Stack developer</small>
      .jumbotron
        h1 Michael Perkhofer
        p.lead Full Stack Developer&nbsp;
          a(href="https://www.quora.com/What-does-the-term-full-stack-programmer-mean", target="_blank") (*)
    div#portfolio
    section#quotemachine
      .container-fluid
        .col-lg-4.col-sm-6.textbox
          h1 Random Quote machine
          p
            | Displays quotes from the&nbsp;
            a(href='http://www.imdb.com/chart/top', target='_blank') top 250 IMDb movies
            |  and presents them in combination with images from&nbsp;
            a(href='https://www.themoviedb.org/', target='_blank') TMDb
            | .
            br
            a.btn.btn-primary(href="https://github.com/mperkh/imdbquotes", target='_blank') <i class="fa fa-github" aria-hidden="true"></i> Source
            a.btn.btn-primary(href="http://codepen.io/mperkh/full/pJmJOM", target='_blank') <i class="fa fa-codepen" aria-hidden="true"></i> Try it
        .col-lg-8.col-sm-6
          img(src='https://s3.amazonaws.com/f623f793d321325d3de5c7f6ff91528-default/fcc/portfolio/quotemachine03.jpg', class="img-responsive img-rounded")
    section#localweather
      .container-fluid
        .col-lg-4.col-sm-6.textbox
          h1 Show the local weather
          ul
            li Shows the local weather using
              a(href="http://forecast.io", target="_blank")  forecastIO
            li Accessing HTML Geolocation API
            li Build using
              a(href="https://facebook.github.io/react/", target="_blank")  reactJS
            li Show current location, using Google Maps
          a.btn.btn-primary(href="https://github.com/mperkh/fcc-weather", target='_blank') <i class="fa fa-github" aria-hidden="true"></i> Source
          a.btn.btn-primary(href="https://codepen.io/mperkh/full/akRWZy/", target='_blank') <i class="fa fa-codepen" aria-hidden="true"></i> Try it
        .col-lg-6.col-sm-4.col-lg-offset-1.col-sm-offset-1
          img(src='https://s3.amazonaws.com/f623f793d321325d3de5c7f6ff91528-default/fcc/portfolio/weather.png', class="img-responsive img-rounded")
    section#calculator
      .container-fluid
        .col-lg-4.col-sm-6.textbox
          h1 Calculator
          ul
            li A javascript version of a
              a(href="http://mycalcdb.free.fr/main.php?l=0&id=2916", targt="_blank")  Braun ET66 aka 4776 version 2
            li Build using
              a(href="https://facebook.github.io/react/", target="_blank")  reactJS
            img(src='https://s3.amazonaws.com/f623f793d321325d3de5c7f6ff91528-default/fcc/portfolio/calculator.gif', class="img-responsive img-rounded")
          a.btn.btn-primary(href="https://github.com/mperkh/fcc-calculator", target='_blank') <i class="fa fa-github" aria-hidden="true"></i> Source
          a.btn.btn-primary(href="http://codepen.io/mperkh/full/QKwQbQ/", target='_blank') <i class="fa fa-codepen" aria-hidden="true"></i> Try it
        .col-lg-6.col-sm-6.col-lg-offset-1
          img(src='https://s3.amazonaws.com/f623f793d321325d3de5c7f6ff91528-default/fcc/portfolio/calculator01.png', class="img-responsive img-rounded")
          img(src='https://s3.amazonaws.com/f623f793d321325d3de5c7f6ff91528-default/fcc/portfolio/calculator02.png', class="img-responsive img-rounded")
    section#simon
      .container-fluid
        .col-lg-4.col-sm-6.textbox
          h1 Simons's Game
          ul
            li Simons's game, using
              a(href="http://brutalistwebsites.com/", target="_blank")  brutalist design
            li Makes use of
              a(href="http://kristopolous.github.io/BOOTSTRA.386/", target="_blank")  bootstra.386
              | , a vintage 1980s DOS inspired Twitter Bootstrap theme.
            li Build using
              a(href="https://facebook.github.io/react/", target="_blank")  reactJS
          a.btn.btn-primary(href="https://github.com/mperkh/fcc-simon", target='_blank') <i class="fa fa-github" aria-hidden="true"></i> Source
          a.btn.btn-primary(href="https://codepen.io/mperkh/full/PGdmWP/", target='_blank') <i class="fa fa-codepen" aria-hidden="true"></i> Try it
        .col-lg-6.col-sm-6.col-lg-offset-1
          img(src='https://s3.amazonaws.com/f623f793d321325d3de5c7f6ff91528-default/fcc/portfolio/simon.png', class="img-responsive img-rounded")
    section#tictactoe
      .container-fluid
        .col-lg-4.col-sm-6.textbox
          h1 Tic Tac Toe
          ul
            li Classic game Tic Tac Toe, written in Javascript and calssic bootstrap theme.
            li The AI is a min/max implementation and it should not be possible to win against the AI.
            li Build using
              a(href="https://facebook.github.io/react/", target="_blank")  reactJS
          a.btn.btn-primary(href="https://github.com/mperkh/fcc-tictactoe", target='_blank') <i class="fa fa-github" aria-hidden="true"></i> Source
          a.btn.btn-primary(href="https://codepen.io/mperkh/full/ozoQVX/", target='_blank') <i class="fa fa-codepen" aria-hidden="true"></i> Try it
        .col-lg-6.col-sm-6.col-lg-offset-1
          img(src='https://s3.amazonaws.com/f623f793d321325d3de5c7f6ff91528-default/fcc/portfolio/tictac.png', class="img-responsive img-rounded")
    section#contact
      .container-fluid
        .col-md-6.col-md-offset-4
          <h1>Contact</h1>
          a(href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/perki2000/", target="_blank") <i class="fa fa-flickr" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          a(href="https://www.facebook.com/michael.perkhofer", target="_blank")  <i class="fa fa-facebook-official" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          a(href="https://twitter.com/perki2000", target="_blank")  <i class="fa fa-twitter-square" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          a(href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mperkh", target="_blank")  <i class="fa fa-linkedin-square" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          a(href="https://github.com/mperkh", target="_blank")  <i class="fa fa-github" aria-hidden="true"></i>







